    "General": {
      "text": "Type: Oxazolidinone\nantibiotic\nDosage Forms: PO/IV\nCommon Trade Names: Zyvox\nBacteriostatic, so prefer another agent in bacteremia, such as\nceftaroline\nin\nvancomycin\nresistant MRSA",
