    "Adult_Dosing": {
      "text": "VRE\ninfections:\n600 mg PO/IV Q12H x 14-28 days\nPneumonia\n, community-acquired:\n600 mg PO/IV Q12H x 5 days\nPneumonia\n, hospital-acquired or ventilator-associated:\n600 mg PO/IV Q12H x 5 days\nUncomplicated\nskin infections\n:\n400 mg PO Q12H x 10-14 days\nComplicated\nskin infections\n:\n600 mg PO/IV Q12H x 10-14 days\nEndocarditis\n600 mg PO/IV Q12H x 6 weeks",
